## ‚≠ê Pro Tip

Switching from **local** to **cloud** to **on-premises** is as easy as:

```python
db = cshelve.open('local.db')
# to
db = cshelve.open('aws-s3.ini')
# to
db = cshelve.open('sftp.ini')
```

**No code rewrite. Just change the config.**
